                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6912" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1731</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8414 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">快慢相宜，攻守自如——青山工业的竞争战略之变</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Appropriate speed with easy attack and defense--The change of competitive strategy of Tsingshan industrial</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">毕茜，郑骁杨，杨笙</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西南大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆青山工业有限责任公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">研发部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">竞争战略；青山工业；新能源汽车</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Tsingshan Industrial;Competitive strategy</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">变速器，被喻为控制着汽车速度与力量分配的“大脑”。重庆青山工业有限责任公司（以下简称青山工业）是一家致力于打造一流变速器的制造企业。经过近六十年的发展，青山工业已经成长为制造国产变速器的标杆企业，在赓续军工精神专精传统产品的同时也积极开拓新能源领域，力求产品创新。本案例以青山工业从选择传统产品差异化竞争战略到新能源产品集中竞争战略为主线，借其面临不同市场格局时由“防守”到“进攻”的节奏转变，详细描绘了青山工业如何巧妙取得传统产品的成功以及对于未来新能源产品的初步规划。本案例为描述性案例，旨在帮助学员理解竞争战略及相关的理论知识，对于学员了解企业在不同环境下如何通过选择适当的竞争战略建立优势同样具有借鉴和启示意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The transmission is known as the &quot;brain&quot; that controls the speed and power distribution of the car. Chongqing Tsingshan industrial Co., Ltd. is a enterprise committed to manufacture first-class transmissions. Tsingshan industrial has grown into a benchmark enterprise for manufacturing domestic transmission. While specializing in traditional products, it also explores the field of new energy and strives for product innovation. This case takes Tsingshan industrial from choosing the differentiated competition strategy of traditional products to the centralized competition strategy of new energy products as the main line, and through the rhythm change from &quot;defense&quot; to &quot;attack&quot;, it describes in detail how Tsingshan industrial obtains the success of traditional products and the preliminary planning for new energy products. This case is a descriptive case aiming to help students understand relevant theoretical knowledge. It also has reference and enlightenment significance for the college to understand how enterprises establish advantages by selecting appropriate competitive strategy in different situations.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">差异化竞争战略理论及其实现的过程；产品生命周期理论以及判断分析；结合实际情况认识开拓市场过程中的两面性；STP理论与集中竞争战略理论的应用；创新理论及相关启示</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-12</td>
                            </tr>
